{"tid":328042,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"我發覺愈廢既人 愈鍾意比較","createTime":"2017-07-19T09:20:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-24T11:29:25.000Z","uid":112627,"like":93,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"03a8586a937ccf2efedc333d1d1f78ee8b0c0091","tid":328042,"uid":112627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T09:20:43.000Z","msg":"果種自卑感勁到呢 咩都要話你唔掂<br />\n明明幾靚仔會話人好柒 柒過金城武<br />\n音樂玩得好就串人玩pop<br />\n讀書讀得好就話人死讀書冇撚用<br />\n<br />\n但同時佢地好介意自己既廢 死都要拿番渣沙<br />\n好似班自資學位撚咁 明知自己死蠢 又唔撚勤力讀 dse考到一舊屎咁都要酸人<br />\n最尾去讀一d明知冇撚用既學店<br />\n讀完一年不知名遙距外國大學post ig fb 同人講：「好撚辛苦終於畢業啦！」<br />\n強行將自己拉去一班勤力入大學既人到<br />\n真係好撚嘔心<br />\n<br />\n如果你勤力入唔到大學我會尊重你，因為讀書唔係唯一出路。<br />\n<br />\n但你就唔好酸人又覺得自己懷才不遇，你咁樣仲衰撚過大陸人。讀d垃圾曬時間曬老豆老母既錢！"},{"pid":"51bbe20ec5e59d83ccbcc1fe0fe932380c892fe0","tid":328042,"uid":42119,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T09:22:49.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"f016d2c0e252bd0a6f9a861caa3dcc067a29f224","tid":328042,"uid":112627,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T09:24:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>閱</blockquote><br />\n希望你唔係其中一個廢物"},{"pid":"ce4105a7b49677771fba9f9ba0681e5b2fab0a14","tid":328042,"uid":60115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T10:00:53.000Z","msg":"樓豬小心比asshole仔咬"},{"pid":"d3ac22d285b9b39bdee8449c96c4980d32e2a92b","tid":328042,"uid":54346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T10:04:31.000Z","msg":"同意 講乜都好似踩到佢地條尾咁 之後就話你廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fef06f6b0587e6040afc85c5cf003f9c2ee3b39","tid":328042,"uid":609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T10:07:08.000Z","msg":"Agger"},{"pid":"c83319a8be847d57b1de152135b524fa760ea65f","tid":328042,"uid":52918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T10:08:18.000Z","msg":"此post將上熱門"},{"pid":"0855bdaff364c6b7655a445c9eaae489d2241a92","tid":328042,"uid":30368,"like":5,"dislike":0